<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM11.5.1">
<l>māṉamaru meṉṉōkki vaitēvi yiṉtuṇaiyā</l>
<l>kāṉamaruṅ kallatarpōyk kāṭuṟaintāṉ kāṇēṭī</l>
<l>kāṉamaruṅ kallatarppōyk kāṭuṟainta poṉṉaṭikaḷ</l>
<l>vāṉavartañ ceṉṉi malarkkaṇṭāy cāḻalē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>See, Friend! As the beloved of Vaidehi, her soft glance like a deer’s,</l>
<l>He dwelled in the forest following craggy paths fit for the jungle.</l>
<l>You see [this]! [Those] golden feet that dwelled in the forest</l>
<l rend="indent">following craggy paths fit for the jungle</l>
<l>Are flowers on the heads of the celestials. Cāḻalē!</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
